Tried downloading but as others have said, the keygen seems to be missing.  I have Corel installed as trial (now expired) so how do I activate?  I know I have to kill internet, but when I select OTHER to activate, Corel fills in two lines, the Installation code and the serial number but leaves activation code blank.  Can someone here or in Suprbay Forum explain... Thanks!

How to activate:

Open the keygen and generate a serial, copy and insert it when asked by corel when installing, don't close the keygen, finish the installation. When corel asks to update, don't let it update. Open corel when finished, click on other acitvation options => phone corel => copy the installation code and paste it to the empty box of the keygen => click activation code => copy the code and paste it to the corel activation code box => click continue and you are finished.
